# Frontend build output
# Note: frontend/dist is NOT committed to git. It is:
#   1. Built automatically during `rake release` (bundled into gem for RubyGems.org)
#   2. Built locally via `bundle exec rake build_frontend` (for development)
# The gem bundles pre-built assets, so end users don't need to build.
